title: TV5Monde Secrets d Histoire 2014 Anne de Bretagne deux fois Rein
description:
Anne de Bretagne deux fois Reine

History Documentary hosted by Stephane Bern, published by TV5Monde broadcasted as part of TV5Monde Secrets d'Histoire series in 2014 - French narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/4/43/Anne-de-Bretagne-deux-fois-Reine-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Anne of Brittany, twice queen.

The life of Anne of Brittany was an extraordinary adventure of love, betrayal, desperation and jealousy. Married at 14 to King Charles VIII, then seven years later to King Louis XII, she united her Duchy with its historic enemy: France.
